        <profileDesc>
            <creation/>
            <abstract>
                <p>A collection of homilies for each day of the Passion Week,
                   different from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1291Dersan">Dǝrsān māḥyawi</ref>, with the exception of the introduction and the first homily.
                 The Ethiopian edition <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/WJDA2HCK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Segesellase1996DersanaMedhane"/><title level="m">ድርሳነ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡ ወገድለ፡ መባዓ፡ ጽዮን፡ በአማርኛና፡ በግዕዝ። &lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;(&lt;/hi&gt;Dǝrsāna Madhāne ʿĀlam wagalda Mabaʿā Ṣǝyon baʾamārǝññānnā bagǝʿǝz, ‘Homiliary of the Saviour of the World and the Acts of Mabaʿā Ṣǝyon, in Amharic and Gǝʿǝz’&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;)&lt;/hi&gt;</title><editor><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Yawāldǝbbit qǝddǝst Māryām ʾandǝnnat gadām</t:name></editor><pubPlace>n.p.</pubPlace><publisher>n.pub.</publisher><date>2003</date></bibl> contains an additional part in the Introduction that is missing in many manuscripts.</p>
            </abstract>
