      <body>
         <div type="bibliography">
            <listBibl type="editions">
               <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/B3MKYNA3"><seg type="thesis"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Kim2009Christologie"/><title level="m">Une christologie vétérotestamentaire? Édition et traduction d’une homélie anonyme éthiopienne (BnF Abb 29 f° 1v-6r, BnF Éth 116 f° 7r-14v)</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sergey</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kim</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><date>2009</date><citedRange unit="page">30-47</citedRange></bibl>
               <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/WJDA2HCK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Segesellase1996DersanaMedhane"/><title level="m">ድርሳነ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡ ወገድለ፡ መባዓ፡ ጽዮን፡ በአማርኛና፡ በግዕዝ። &lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;(&lt;/hi&gt;Dǝrsāna Madhāne ʿĀlam wagalda Mabaʿā Ṣǝyon baʾamārǝññānnā bagǝʿǝz, ‘Homiliary of the Saviour of the World and the Acts of Mabaʿā Ṣǝyon, in Amharic and Gǝʿǝz’&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;)&lt;/hi&gt;</title><editor><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Yawāldǝbbit qǝddǝst Māryām ʾandǝnnat gadām</t:name></editor><pubPlace>n.p.</pubPlace><publisher>n.pub.</publisher><date>2003</date><citedRange unit="page">23-97</citedRange></bibl>
                 </listBibl>
            </div>
          <div type="edition">
          <note>The division into text parts follows <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet116">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 116</ref>.</note>
          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Introduction" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6616HomilyPassionIntro">
             <label>Introduction</label>
             <ab>
               <pb n="6r"/>
                 <cb n="a"/><l n="1"><hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሥሉስ፡ ዘእንበለ፡</hi> ቅድም፡ ወተድኅሮ፡</l>
                 <l n="2">በግጻዌሁ፡ ይትረአ<hi rend="rubric">ይ፡ ዘአስተዋሀደ፡ ምክሮ።</hi></l>
                 <l n="3"><hi rend="rubric">በጠፈረ፡ በረ</hi>ድ፡ ወነድ፡ ዘሐነፀ፡ ማኅደሮ።</l>
                 <l n="4">ወበአርእስተ፡ ኪሩቤል፡ ርቱዓ፡ ዘአማዕዘነ፡ መንበሮ፡</l>
             </ab>
          </div>

          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Monday" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6617PassionsHomilyMonday">
             <label>Homily for Holy Monday</label>
             <ab>
               <pb n="7r"/>
                 <cb n="a"/><l n="1">ናንቅሕ፡ ርእሰ፡ ሕሊናነ፡</l> 
                 <l n="2">ወናስተሐውስ፡ አስራወ፡ ልሳንነ፡</l> 
                 <l n="3">ንክሥት፡ አፉነ፡</l> 
                 <l n="4">ወናስተናብብ፡ ከናፍሪነ፡</l>
                 <l n="5">ከመ፡ ንንግር፡ ዜና፡ ሕማማቲሁ፡ ለመድኃኒነ፨</l>
             </ab>
             </div>

          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="HomilyTuesday">
          <label>Homily for Holy Tuesday</label>
          <ab>
            <pb n="14v"/>
              <cb n="b"/><hi rend="rubric">ንግባእኬ፡ ከመ፡ ንፈጽም፡ ዜና፡ ሕማሙ፡</hi> ለመድኃኒነ፡
              ወአንግሁ፡ ይእተ፡ ኵላ፡ ሌሊተ፡ እንዘ፡ ይዘብጥዎ፡ ወይጸፍዕዎ፡
          </ab>
          </div>

              <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="HomilyTuesdayOther">
                  <label>Another homily for Holy Tuesday</label>
                  <note>This homily is not attested in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet116">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 116</ref> and most of the wittnesses of 
                      <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6193HomiliaryPassions">Dǝrsāna madḫāne ʿālam element TEI with id LIT6193HomiliaryPassions</ref>, but in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient8819">London, British Library, BL Oriental 8819</ref>.</note>
                  <ab>
                      ወእምድኅረዝ፡ እንዘ፡ ሀሎ፡ በቤተ፡ ስምዖን፡ ዘከመ፡ አቅረቡ፡ ድራረ፡ 
                      ወዘከመ፡ ወሀበ፡ ሥጋሁ፡ ወደሞ፡ ለአርዳኢሁ፡ ወዘከመ፡ ሐፀበ፡ እገሪሆሙ፡ ወዘከመ፡ አውተረ፡ 
                      ጸልዮ፡ ኵሉ፡ ጽሑፍ፡ ሀሎ፡ ውስተ፡ ወንጌል። <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                  </ab>
              </div>

          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="HomilyWednesday">
          <label>Homily for Holy Wednesday</label>
          <ab>
            <pb n="19v"/>
              <cb n="a"/><hi rend="rubric">ንግባዕኬ፡ ከመ፡ ንፈጽም፡ ነገረ፡ ወበጊዜ፡</hi> ፱ሰዓት፡ ተከሥተ፡ ፀሐይ፡ በዓውደ፡ ሰማይ፨
          </ab>
          </div>

          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="HomilyThursday">
          <label>Homily for Maundy Thursday</label>
          <ab>
            <pb n="25v"/>
            <cb n="b"/><hi rend="rubric">ንግባዕኬ፡ ከመ፡ ንፈጽም፡ ነገረ፡ ዘ፱ሰዓት፡</hi>
            ወይእተ፡ ጊዜ፡ ሶበ፡ ርእዩ፡ ነቢያት፡ ቀደምት፡ ወአበው፡ ቀደምት፡
          </ab>
          </div>

          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="HomilyFriday">
          <label>Homily for Good Friday</label>
          <ab>
            <pb n="29v"/>
            <cb n="b"/><hi rend="rubric">ንግባዕኬ፡ ከመ፡ ንፈጽም፡ ነገረ፡ ዘምሴተ፡</hi>
            ዓርበ፡ እስመ፡ ይቤ፡ ዘካርያስ፡ ይእቲ፡ ዕለት፡ እምብርት፡ በኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ኢኮነት፡
          </ab>
          </div>

          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="HomilySaturday">
          <label>Homily for Holy Saturday</label>
          <ab>
            <pb n="33r"/>
            <cb n="a"/>ንንግርኬ፡ ኅዳጠ፡ ዜናሁ፡ ለፀልቦ፡ <hi rend="rubric">መድኃኒነ፡</hi>
            መስቀል፡ ዘከመ፡ ተብህለ፡ ሀሎ፡ ምስለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እምቀድመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ፍጥረት፡
          </ab>
          </div>

          <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="HomilySunday">
          <label>Homily for Passion Sunday</label>
          <ab>
            <pb n="35r"/>
            <cb n="a"/>ንግባዕኬ፡ ከመ፡ ንሰብሖ፡ ወንወድሶ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡
            እንዘ፡ ንብል፡ ጥዑመ፡ ስም፡ መድኃኒነ፡ ለሊሁ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወእሙ፡ መቅደስ፡ ወመስቀሉ፡ አትሮንስ፡
          </ab>
          </div>

          </div>

                

        </body>
    </text></TEI>